title: The allure of island life at Martha’s Vineyard (VIDEO)
text:
The allure of island life at Martha’s Vineyard (VIDEO) Thursday July 30, 2015 Print Article 
MARTHA'S VINEYARD, July 30 — Lobster on the deck, sunset on the beach and long nights on the town are all part of Martha’s Vineyard island allure. — New York Times A general view of gingerbread cottages in the Martha's Vineyard Campmeeting Association, Oak Bluffs, Massachusetts in this undated handout photo provided to Reuters October 18, 2012. — Reuters pic More Stories for You:
